Next Steps Updated: another meeting to review

issues post upgrade will likely need separate ticket to open then close for internal issue tracking

What We've Learned Updated: upgrade completed but the FSAA scan jobs are behaving strangely post upgrade
most servers finished but 6 are still "running" but duration is blank

zoom meeting

 

no running instances

task stats shows the scans of some servers as "running" but the duration is zero

 

checked the jobs folder and found the running.lck file was still there

confirmed no jobs running

deleted it

 

client does have overlapping FS jobs scheduled so it's possible one got in the way of the other but the client says he's had the daily scan disabled since the upgrade

 

started FS collection again

client will let us know how it goes.

What We've Learned Updated: upgrade completed but the FSAA scan jobs are behaving strangely post upgrade
